name: #SACRIFICE#
description:
acrificing our real life for a
virtual one is nowadays a real
concern. There is no limit on how
much time we dedicate in social
networks, to our followers, to our
haters, and especially to fulfill
our ego with infinite likes and
flattering comments. The daily
dose we take keeps growing
without limits like drug tolerance
in drug addicts. Meanwhile the
real people around us, our
friends and family are becoming
less interesting and pushed to a
second plane.
